description: This vector polygon/s layer  was sourced from the World Conservation Monitoring Center (WCMC) as a global layer and used to derive the WIO MPAs . It shows marine designated areas where human activities are restricted for conservation purposes.
keywords: MPA, Western Indian Ocean, Africa, East Africa, Comoros, Kenya, Madagascar, Mauritius, Mayotte, Mozambique, Reunion, Seychelles, Somalia, United Republic of Tanzania, Southern Africa, South Africa
name: WIO Marine Protected Area
